      <div class="ahmad-aligner-item">
                    <h1>- Location-Based Weather App with Geolocation and Dynamic Visuals</h1>
        <p>
         We created a location-based weather application that fetches current weather conditions and forecasts using a public weather API. To personalize the experience, we integrated geolocation services, allowing the app to automatically detect the user’s location. Our team designed dynamic visuals that change according to weather conditions and implemented offline caching and error handling to maintain performance even with limited connectivity.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
